author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Today was Rushia's return to Minecraft, later of a tragedy. 
That means, it's not lost after all, because at starting she faced against the god creeper, later of too many disgraceful events when she lost Tsurupettachi Kai (Special pickaxe) and the Tsurugi no Mai (One of special tridents) about months ago.
Finally she obtained the Creeper's head. 

But about the title stream... The problem is about how to compensate these zenloss... 

Finally she decided to work, but another problem was presented: in what? If at Subaru's building or at Usada's kensetsu...
Personally talking, I always was thinking in a possible Rushia's buildings... Emmm... Not that... Since she collected Daiya or Diamonds (And in one of these streams she caught emeralds) I was thinking on a Diamond extraction industry... Or better... "Rushia's Minerals"

But for now, she made a Holoserver's exploration, since Kiara Fried Phoenix and Pekora-san's Pekoland, and also Haachama's deadly Rollercoaster and Tsunomaki Watame-san's Jankenpon item vault. 

:_ãƒãƒ¼ãƒˆ: 3:34:25 and 3:45:31 Personal Marks
Especially the first, with the line: "I will stand by you" from her song "Iris"
